  "text": [
    "We have",
    "a map of the universe",
    "for microbes,",
    "we have",
    "a map of a microbe",
    "for the universe.",
    "we have",
    "a Grand Master of chess",
    "made of electronic circuits.",
    "But above all",
    "we have",
    "the ability",
    "to sort peas,",
    "to cup water in our hands,",
    "to seek",
    "the right screw",
    "under the sofa",
    "for hours",
    "This",
    "gives us",
    "wings."
  ],
  "title": "Wings",
  "year": ""
}